<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Overall dorsal view A Johora intermedia Ng, 1986, holotype male (19.8 x 15.1 mm) (ZRC 1984.6529), Pahang B J. tahanensis (Bott, 1966), male (30.7 x 25.5 mm) (ZRC 1984.6795), Pahang C J. thoi Ng, 1990, holotype male (41.2 x 33.3 mm) (ZRC 1989.2249), Terengganu D J. hoiseni Ng & Takeda, 1992, holotype male (25.1 x 21.1 mm) (ZRC 1984.6673), Kelantan E J. thaiana Leelawathanagoon, Lheknim & Ng, 2005, paratype male (22.2 x 18.6 mm) (ZRC 2006.0052), Thailand F J. booliati sp. nov., holotype male (34.6 x 30.0 mm) (ZRC 2020.0072), Pahang G J. erici sp. nov., holotype male (38.3 x 32.0 mm) (ZRC 2020.0360), Perak H J. michaeli sp. nov., holotype male (22.7 x 19.2 mm) (ZRC 2010.0047), Terengganu." , "Figure 10. A-D Johora thaiana Leelawathanagoon, Lheknim & Ng, 2005, paratype male (22.2 x 18.6 mm) (ZRC 2006.0052), Thailand E-I J. booliati sp. nov., holotype male (34.6 x 30.0 mm) (ZRC 2020.0072), Pahang A, E left G 1 (ventral view) B, F distal part of left G 1 (ventral view) C, H distal part of left G 1 (dorsal view) G distal part of left G 1 (mesial view) D, I left G 2 (ventral view). Scale bas: 1.0 mm (A, D, E, I); 0.5 mm (B, C, F-H)." , "Figure 12. Overall dorsal view A Johora intermedia Ng, 1986, female (17.9 x 14.7 mm) (ZRC 2001.1002), Selangor B J. tahanensis (Bott, 1966), female (24.4 x 21.0 mm) (ZRC 1984.6765), Pahang C J. thoi Ng, 1990, female (31.7 x 25.5 mm) (ZRC 2001.1167), Terengganu D J. hoiseni Ng & Takeda, 1992, paratype female (22.1 x 19.0 mm) (ZRC 1984.6675), Kelantan E J. thaiana Leelawathanagoon, Lheknim & Ng, 2005, paratype female (21.0 x 17.4 mm) (ZRC 2006.0053), Thailand F J. booliati sp. nov., paratype female (40.4 x 34.4 mm) (ZRC 1995.270), Pahang G J. erici sp. nov., paratype female (32.8 x 26.9 mm) (ZRC 1995.268), Perak H J. michaeli sp. nov., paratype female (29.9 x 25.0 mm) (ZRC 2010.0047), Terengganu." , "Figure 14. Sternopleonal cavity and vulvae A Johora intermedia Ng, 1986, female (17.9 x 14.7 mm) (ZRC 2001.1002), Selangor B J. tahanensis (Bott, 1966), female (24.4 x 21.0 mm) (ZRC 1984.6765), Pahang C J. thoi Ng, 1990, female (31.7 x 25.5 mm) (ZRC 2001.1167), Terengganu D J. hoiseni Ng & Takeda, 1992, paratype female (22.1 x 19.0 mm) (ZRC 1984.6675), Kelantan E J. thaiana Leelawathanagoon, Lheknim & Ng, 2005, paratype female (21.0 x 17.4 mm) (ZRC 2006.0053), Thailand F J. booliati sp. nov., paratype female (40.4 x 34.4 mm) (ZRC 1995.270), Pahang G J. erici sp. nov., paratype female (32.8 x 26.9 mm) (ZRC 1995.268), Perak H J. michaeli sp. nov., paratype female (29.9 x 25.0 mm) (ZRC 2010.0047), Terengganu." , "Figure 3. Frontal view of cephalothorax A Johora intermedia Ng, 1986, holotype male (19.8 x 15.1 mm) (ZRC 1984.6529), Pahang B J. tahanensis (Bott, 1966), male (30.7 x 25.5 mm) (ZRC 1984.6795), Pahang C J. thoi Ng, 1990, holotype male (41.2 x 33.3 mm) (ZRC 1989.2249), Terengganu D J. hoiseni Ng & Takeda, 1992, holotype male (25.1 x 21.1 mm) (ZRC 1984.6673), Kelantan E J. thaiana Leelawathanagoon, Lheknim & Ng, 2005, paratype male (22.2 x 18.6 mm) (ZRC 2006.0052), Thailand F J. booliati sp. nov., holotype male (34.6 x 30.0 mm) (ZRC 2020.0072), Pahang G J. erici sp. nov., holotype male (38.3 x 32.0 mm) (ZRC 2020.0360), Perak H J. michaeli sp. nov., holotype male (22.7 x 19.2 mm) (ZRC 2010.0047), Terengganu." , "Figure 5. Anterior thoracic sternum and pleon A Johora intermedia Ng, 1986, holotype male (19.8 x 15.1 mm) (ZRC 1984.6529), Pahang B J. tahanensis (Bott, 1966), male (30.7 x 25.5 mm) (ZRC 1984.6795), Pahang C J. thoi Ng, 1990, holotype male (41.2 x 33.3 mm) (ZRC 1989.2249), Terengganu D J. hoiseni Ng & Takeda, 1992, holotype male (25.1 x 21.1 mm) (ZRC 1984.6673), Kelantan E J. thaiana Leelawathanagoon, Lheknim & Ng, 2005, paratype male (22.2 x 18.6 mm) (ZRC 2006.0052), Thailand F J. booliati sp. nov., holotype male (34.6 x 30.0 mm) (ZRC 2020.0072), Pahang G J. erici sp. nov., holotype male (38.3 x 32.0 mm) (ZRC 2020.0360), Perak H J. michaeli sp. nov., holotype male (22.7 x 19.2 mm) (ZRC 2010.0047), Terengganu." , "Figure 13. Female pleon A Johora intermedia Ng, 1986, female (17.9 x 14.7 mm) (ZRC 2001.1002), Selangor B J. tahanensis (Bott, 1966), female (24.4 x 21.0 mm) (ZRC 1984.6765), Pahang C J. thoi Ng, 1990, female (31.7 x 25.5 mm) (ZRC 2001.1167), Terengganu D J. hoiseni Ng & Takeda, 1992, paratype female (22.1 x 19.0 mm) (ZRC 1984.6675), Kelantan E J. thaiana Leelawathanagoon, Lheknim & Ng, 2005, paratype female (21.0 x 17.4 mm) (ZRC 2006.0053), Thailand F J. booliati sp. nov., paratype female (40.4 x 34.4 mm) (ZRC 1995.270), Pahang G J. erici sp. nov., paratype female (32.8 x 26.9 mm) (ZRC 1995.268), Perak H J. michaeli sp. nov., paratype female (29.9 x 25.0 mm) (ZRC 2010.0047), Terengganu." , "Figure 2. Dorsal view of carapace A Johora intermedia Ng, 1986, holotype male (19.8 x 15.1 mm) (ZRC 1984.6529), Pahang B J. tahanensis (Bott, 1966), male (30.7 x 25.5 mm) (ZRC 1984.6795), Pahang C J. thoi Ng, 1990, holotype male (41.2 x 33.3 mm) (ZRC 1989.2249) Terengganu D J. hoiseni Ng & Takeda, 1992, holotype male (25.1 x 21.1 mm) (ZRC 1984.6673), Kelantan E J. thaiana Leelawathanagoon, Lheknim & Ng, 2005, paratype male (22.2 x 18.6 mm) (ZRC 2006.0052), Thailand F J. booliati sp. nov., holotype male (34.6 x 30.0 mm) (ZRC 2020.0072), Pahang G J. erici sp. nov., holotype male (38.3 x 32.0 mm) (ZRC 2020.0360), Perak H J. michaeli sp. nov., holotype male (22.7 x 19.2 mm) (ZRC 2010.0047), Terengganu." , "Figure 4. Left third maxilliped A Johora intermedia Ng, 1986, holotype male (19.8 x 15.1 mm) (ZRC 1984.6529), Pahang B J. tahanensis (Bott, 1966), male (30.7 x 25.5 mm) (ZRC 1984.6795), Pahang C J. thoi Ng, 1990, holotype male (41.2 x 33.3 mm) (ZRC 1989.2249), Terengganu D J. hoiseni Ng & Takeda, 1992, holotype male (25.1 x 21.1 mm) (ZRC 1984.6673), Kelantan E J. thaiana Leelawathanagoon, Lheknim & Ng, 2005, paratype male (22.2 x 18.6 mm) (ZRC 2006.0052), Thailand F J. booliati sp. nov., holotype male (34.6 x 30.0 mm) (ZRC 2020.0072), Pahang G J. erici sp. nov., holotype male (38.3 x 32.0 mm) (ZRC 2020.0360), Perak H J. michaeli sp. nov., holotype male (22.7 x 19.2 mm) (ZRC 2010.0047), Terengganu." , "Figure 9. A-D Johora thoi Ng, 1990, holotype male (41.2 x 33.3 mm) (ZRC 1989.2249), Terengganu E-H J. thoi Ng, 1990, male (21.1 x 17.7 mm) (ZRC 2001.1167), Terengganu I-L J. michaeli sp. nov., holotype male (22.7 x 19.2 mm) (ZRC 2020.0361), Terengganu A, E, I left G 1 (ventral view) B, F, J distal part of left G 1 (ventral view) C, G, K distal part of left G 1 (dorsal view) D, H, L left G 2 (ventral view) A-D after Ng (1990: fig. 2 A, C-E). Scale bars: 1.0 mm (A, D, E, H, I, L); 0.5 mm (B, C, F, G, J, K)." , "Figure 8. A-D Johora tahanensis (Bott, 1966), male (30.7 x 25.5 mm) (ZRC 1984.6795), Pahang E-H J. hoiseni Ng & Takeda, 1992, holotype male (25.1 x 21.1 mm) (ZRC 1984.6673), Kelantan A, E left G 1 (ventral view) B, F distal part of left G 1 (ventral view) C, G distal part of left G 1 (dorsal view) D, H left G 2 (ventral view) E-H after Ng and Takeda (1992: fig. 3 B, D-F). Scale bars: 1.0 mm (A, D, E, H); 0.5 mm (B, C, F, G)." , "Figure 7. Johora erici sp. nov., male (41.2 x 33.8 mm) (ZRC 1995.0269), Kelantan A overall dorsal view B dorsal view of carapace C frontal view of cephalothorax D anterior thoracic sternum and pleon." , "Figure 15. Distribution of species of the Johora tahanensis species group 1 J. tahanensis (Bott, 1966) 2 J. thoi Ng, 1990 3 J. hoiseni Ng & Takeda, 1992 4 J. thaiana Leelawathanagoon, Lheknim & Ng, 2005 5 J. booliati sp. nov. 6 J. erici sp. nov. 7 J. michaeli sp. nov. Map data 2020 Google." , "Figure 11. A-D Johora erici sp. nov., holotype male (38.3 x 32.0 mm) (ZRC 2020.0360), Perak E-H J. erici sp. nov., male (41.2 x 33.8 mm) (ZRC 1995.0269), Kelantan A, E left G 1 (ventral view) B, F distal part of left G 1 (ventral view) C, G distal part of left G 1 (dorsal view) D, H left G 2 (ventral view). Scale bars: 1.0 mm (A, D, E, H); 0.5 mm (B, C, F, G)." ;
